      "writtenOn": "2020-02-27T18:57:10Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "I proposed to replace the taskCountMetric by this rowCounter not because they are tracking the same thing, but we can use them to achieve the same goal: to make sure the tasks are being processed properly.\n\nIIRC, we add taskCountMetric so that we can add an alert later which should notify us when seeing accumulating backlog.  And I think rowCounter can help on that. Even better it can also alert us when the inserts count drops drastically.",
