      "message": "i think a cumulative counter can be used to detect drops in task processing (state delta), but i don\u0027t think it can be used to reason about current current (absolute state). resultdb/task/count is a non-cumulative metric\n\nhow would tell the size of the backlog with a cumulative metric?",
